(88, 4, '2014-01-21 18:34:48', 'PHP 5.4 Patch Now Available', 'Magento is advancing its platform and making development more efficient by adding support for PHP 5.4. Patches are available for download at www.magentocommerce.com/download and you can learn more about this update in our blog post at http://www.magentocommerce.com/blog/comments/magento-now-supports-php-54 .', 'http://www.magentocommerce.com/blog/comments/magento-now-supports-php-54', 0, 0),
