INSERT INTO `#__catalog_product_entity_text` (`value_id`, `entity_type_id`, `attribute_id`, `store_id`, `entity_id`, `value`) VALUES
(1, 4, 72, 0, 1, '<p>The clock is 12" in diameter.\r\nThe clock is assembled with a new quartz clock movement.\r\nThere''s a heavy duty hanger on the back for hanging.\r\nThe clock takes one "AA" battery ( included).</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThis bold chevron vinyl record wall clock makes a bold statement in any room in your home. The chevron pattern dates back to heraldry, or the fabrication of coat of arms. Today, the chevron print is a contemporary choice to enliven your space. Custom handmade from a vinyl record, it is an eco-friendly timing solution that you can feel good about. This vibrant wall clock will give your space a modern elegance that is full of energy. It makes a riveting gift for that style star in your life. This is a limited edition Shannybeebo original design. Order now. \r\n</p>'),
(2, 4, 73, 0, 1, '<ul><li>Handmade item</li><li>Materials: vinyl record, quartz clock</li><li>Made to order</li><li>Feedback: 369, 100% positive.</li><li>Ships worldwide from United States</li></ul>\r\n<div class="name"><strong>About Shannybeebo:</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Shannon: owner, maker, designer, Clock Maker, Marble Baker, Recycler Extraordinaire</li>\r\n<li>She''s Shannon, a San Antonio based artist, who focuses on recycled pieces for home and fashion.</li>\r\n<li>Her specialty is paper art incorporating time pieces, jewelry and home accents.</li>\r\n<li>Her style is upbeat and contemporary.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(3, 4, 83, 0, 1, NULL),
(4, 4, 106, 0, 1, NULL),
(13, 4, 72, 0, 2, '<p>You have the option to add another design or color to the other side of the clock. Please message me with details and color requests. I have several colors and designs to choose from, so if you love the idea, simply send me a convo and we can create a clock unique to your style.</p>\r\n<p>This clock has beautiful gold hands, please let me know if you would like a different set or color. </p>'),
(14, 4, 73, 0, 2, 'This modern wall clock will add a very unique touch to any space! This clock has beautiful bohemian designs which will add a unique flair to your home dÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â©cor. This clock is Eco-friendly which adds to it''s charm. if you love color and design, this clock is the one for you!\r\n<div class="name"><strong>About Shannybeebo:</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Shannon: owner, maker, designer, Clock Maker, Marble Baker, Recycler Extraordinaire</li>\r\n<li>She''s Shannon, a San Antonio based artist, who focuses on recycled pieces for home and fashion.</li>\r\n<li>Her specialty is paper art incorporating time pieces, jewelry and home accents.</li>\r\n<li>Her style is upbeat and contemporary.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(15, 4, 83, 0, 2, NULL),
(16, 4, 106, 0, 2, NULL),
(21, 4, 72, 0, 3, '<p>Brighten up a dull room in your home with this vibrant retro decorative wall clock. Custom handcrafted from two vinyl records, this designer wall clock is unlike anything youÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢ll find in stores. Each record has been meticulously covered in bright retro themed papers and both are connected to form one clock. Jet-black mechanisms complete the look while adding a measure of elegance. This clock is sure to complement any room in your home. It also looks positively stunning when hung in an office. YouÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢ll feel a burst of joyous energy each time you look at it. It also makes an imaginative gift for a friend or relative. It is a limited edition Shannybeebo original. Order now.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nAnd remember that at Shannybeebo, I specialize in creating works of functional art to enhance your space. If you donÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢t see a clock that fulfills your design needs, send me a convo and I will work with you to create your own clock according to your design specifications.\r\n</p>'),
(22, 4, 73, 0, 3, 'Hang this unique clock in any room to instantly brighten up the space.</br>\r\nThis clock is 12" in diameter.</br>\r\nThe clock is assembled with a new quartz clock movement.</br>\r\nThere''s a heavy duty hanger on the back for hanging.</br\r\nThe clock takes one "AA" battery ( included).</br>\r\n<div class="name"><strong>About Shannybeebo:</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Shannon: owner, maker, designer, Clock Maker, Marble Baker, Recycler Extraordinaire</li>\r\n<li>She''s Shannon, a San Antonio based artist, who focuses on recycled pieces for home and fashion.</li>\r\n<li>Her specialty is paper art incorporating time pieces, jewelry and home accents.</li>\r\n<li>Her style is upbeat and contemporary.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(23, 4, 83, 0, 3, NULL),
(24, 4, 106, 0, 3, NULL),
(33, 4, 72, 0, 4, '<p>This unique wall clock will look beautiful in your kitchen, or any room in your home. The bright and beautiful colors really stand out which makes this clock so beautiful and unique. There are shiny gold and hot pink flower designs covering beautiful shades of teal and other shades of blue. The gold, blue and pink colors are sure to brighten your day. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nAnd remember that at Shannybeebo, I specialize in creating works of functional art to enhance your space. If you donÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢t see a clock that fulfills your design needs, send me a convo and I will work with you to create your own clock according to your design specifications.\r\n</p>'),
(34, 4, 73, 0, 4, '<p>\r\nThis beautiful wall clock is a perfect example of boho chic. The back of the clock is not painted. If you would like the back painted, please let me know when you place your order. \r\n</p>'),
(35, 4, 83, 0, 4, NULL),
(36, 4, 106, 0, 4, NULL),
(59, 4, 72, 0, 5, '<p>Do you need a little whimsical dÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â©cor in your home? This small wall clock fits the bill! wall clock will This colorful little clock will look fantastic in any room! Add a little Eco-friendly charm to your home or office with this colorful clock. The front of the clock is covered in different designs and small button prints. I added some chocolate brown painted symbols in the 12, 3, 6 and 9 spots just to add a little more whimsy. This clock really will fit well with any home dÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â©cor! </p>\r\n<p>\r\nThis clock comes with a heavy duty hanger on the back</br>\r\nRequires one AA battery (included)</br>\r\nClock is 10'' in diameter.</br\r\n</p>\r\n'),
(60, 4, 73, 0, 5, '<p>This clock will be made in small quantities, so order while you can. The design is bright and fun and will add a fresh look to your home or office dÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â©cor. This clock (as most) can be made 12" or 10"in. Please feel free to contact me with questions.</p>\r\n<p>The hands are black and red, please let me know if you would like a different style or design.</p>\r\n<p>The back of the clock is not painted. Please let me know if you would like the back of your clock painted.</p>'),
(61, 4, 83, 0, 5, NULL),
(62, 4, 106, 0, 5, NULL),
(67, 4, 72, 0, 6, '<p>This retro wall clock will look great in your kitchen, living room, office..or anywhere you plan to hang it. If you aren''t afraid of some sparkle, this retro gold wall clock is the one for you.</p>\r\n<p>This clock is ready to ship and will be made in very few quantities.</p>\r\n<p>I used long black hands, please let me know if you would like a different color or style. The back of the clock is not painted. If you would like the back painted, please let me know when you place your order.</p>\r\n'),
